      This file contains the detailed list of the user visible changes in
      Mahogany, you can use it to find all important changes between releases.
      Please refer to the cvs update list archives for the even more detailed
      list of all changes.

      See at the end of file for the list of contributors (initials appearing
      in the second column of the changelog below).

Release 0.67 'Constance' ??? ??, 2004
------------------------------------

13.08.04 VZ: "Show MIME Structure" allows to save multiple attachments at once
17.07.04 VZ: full support for showing PGP/MIME encoded messages
17.07.04 VZ: added "Send now" command to the composer "Compose" menu
16.07.04 VZ: show threading indicator in the status column
12.07.04 VZ: use plain, not encrypted, text in replies to PGP messages
11.07.04 VZ: integrated DSPAM statistical spam filter
06.07.04 VZ: "Set From from To" option now behaves more usefully
02.07.04 VZ: added nop() filter action (stop processing the filter program)
15.05.04 VZ: added spam filter for dangerous (executable) attachments
14.05.04 XN: added support for uuencoded attachments
12.05.04 VZ: fixed bug with slashes and colons not working in the user names
22.04.04 VZ: improved signature/trailer detection when replying to messages
21.04.04 VZ: show subfolders not in the tree in bold in browse subfolders dialog
20.04.04 VZ: added "--import" command line option
19.04.04 VZ: made "Quick filter" dialog slightly easier to use
08.04.04 VZ: close the message view window if underlying message is deleted
14.03.04 VZ: highlight the options with non default values in the options dialog
13.03.04 VZ: folders can now be dragged in the tree to change their order

